    {
      "content": "To provide basic settings for the configuration policy",
      "pos": [
        1946,
        2000
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        2006,
        2141
      ],
      "content": "In the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Microsoft Intune administration console<ept id=\"p1\">](https://manage.microsoft.com)</ept>, click <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Policy<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> &amp;gt; <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Overview<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> &amp;gt; <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>Add Policy<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept>."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        2147,
        2229
      ],
      "content": "Click <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Android<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> &amp;gt; <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>General Configuration<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> and then click <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Create Policy<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept>."
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        2237,
        2352
      ],
      "content": "[!NOTE]\nYou cannot create a configuration policy using recommended settings. You must create a custom policy.",
      "leadings": [
