      ],
      "content": "In the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>General<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> section of the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Create Policy<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> page, specify a name and a description for the new policy."
    },
    {
      "content": "Use the information in the following sections to help you supply settings for the policy.",
